collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `b`.`id`, `b`.`patient_id`, `b`.`bill_type`, `b`.`total_amount`, `b`.`description`, `b`.`created_at` as `expense_date`, COALESCE(b.invoice_number, CONCAT("INV-", YEAR(b.created_at), "-", LPAD(b.id, 4, "0"))) as invoice_number, CONCAT(p.first_name, " ", COALESCE(p.middle_name, ""), " ", p.last_name) as patient_name FROM `bills` `b` LEFT JOIN `patients` `p` ON `p`.`id` = `b`.`patient_id` WHERE YEAR(b.created_at) = '2025' ORDER BY `b`.`created_at` DESC
